ingredient: 2 chipotle peppers in adobo sauce (1 Tbsp sauce)
1/8 tsp salt, plus more to taste
2 Tbsp finely chopped cilantro (plus a few whole leaves for garnish)
1 cup long grain rice, rinsed until water runs clear
1 tsp Everything Bagel seasoning plus more for garnish
1/4 cup neutral cooking oil for frying
